{"tid":1136210,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國參議員擬立法 抗衡中國主導電動車供應鏈","createTime":"2019-05-03T00:25:14.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-06T10:19:55.000Z","uid":141151,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"a8fad10614de6c234e81f2e2894c313d0de962ea","tid":1136210,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T00:25:14.000Z","msg":"美國參議員擬立法 抗衡中國主導電動車供應鏈<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2128058\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Flanding%2FmobArticle2%2Fid%2F2128058&d=YcIJTvf9PmU%2BR6jslv3gjMWiAETkOtN%2FvKUl8N5Dwlc%3D&h=4f8e4951\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/landing/mobArticle2/id/2128058</a><br />\n<br />\n美國有國會參議員計劃提出法案，簡化在美國本土發展鋰、石墨等電動車所須原材料的規管，以抗衡中國在有關領域的主導地位。<br />\n<br />\n國會參議院能源及天然資源委員會主席Lisa Murkowski接受路透訪問時表示，計劃與另一名參議員Joe Manchin共同提出相關法案，以免美國的電動車業務受制於由中國控制的原材料供應鏈。<br />\n<br />\n中國現時是全球最大的鋰供應國，產量相當於全球需求量的三分之二，美國產量只佔全球5%。鋰是鋰電池必須的原材料，鋰電池則是電動車必須的組件。"},{"pid":"9f7059bbfb4560eb8e84413e60beba328715e7e0","tid":1136210,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T00:51:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"875a6004057ed025fbf0b32bd977a4f5bfb2454a","tid":1136210,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T14:06:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a07cbb4cba6157efa51c9dd6cbf156e45e3dc60","tid":1136210,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T00:19:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2b4252e0f223eed490c43d0d89f961bf1914bc98","tid":1136210,"uid":14433,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T00:22:53.000Z","msg":"美國人終於醒覺了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"caa19f8c4b6fcbb7242279508dd71a41e9556de3","tid":1136210,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-06T10:19:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}